instruction: Conduct a comprehensive analysis of the common risk factors that drive performance across all asset classes, including real estate.
output: To conduct a comprehensive analysis of common risk factors across all asset classes, including real estate, we will need to gather extensive data and utilize advanced analytical techniques beyond traditional sector and geography-based performance attribution. This analysis will provide a deeper understanding of factors that distinguish winners and losers in today's rapidly changing business landscape. Additionally, we will need to identify unique risk factors present in real estate markets that impact overall performance. This analysis will help investors make strategic decisions and ultimately drive better long-term performance.
